{"tid":2386975,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"林伯落「車」袋200萬鎊，油王炒領隊已用1.1億鎊","createTime":"2021-01-30T03:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T17:19:30.000Z","uid":31314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"51c1095022938af686b7aa2d4df9073d747673a2","tid":2386975,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T03:16:44.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒指，林柏特被車路士解僱所得的賠償是200萬鎊，而車仔班主阿巴莫域治歷來送走主帥所花的數目已經累積至<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">1.125億鎊</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n林柏特（Frank Lampard）周一慘被車路士班主阿巴莫域治（Roman Abramovich）請食「無情雞」，外間估計他將可獲得高達600萬鎊的巨額補償。然而，英國《每日郵報》透露，基於車仔還未向林伯提供新約，而其舊合約就只餘下最後6個月，因此他實際所得的賠償額就只有200萬鎊，遠低於外界預期。 說到林柏特，他已是阿巴莫域治買入車路士以來，第13位離任的領隊。《每日郵報》為阿巴作出統計，他歷來花錢送走的主帥共有9人（摩連奴兩次），<strong><span class=\"red\">只有賓尼迪斯、軒迪克和沙利離任是不費一毫</span></strong>，花費已累計達1.125億鎊。 9人當中，以摩連奴兩次落「車」收獲最豐，合共取走了阿巴莫域治3140萬鎊，其次是干地的2660萬鎊，但干地個人就只是袋走了900萬鎊，其餘的金錢則是用作教練團隊遣散費和法律費用。而林柏特則是阿巴莫域治炒主帥以來，炒得最慳家的一位。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>ROLL-CALL OF ROMAN ABRAMOVICH'S SACKINGS </strong><br />\n<br />\nMay 2004: Claudio Ranieri - &pound;6million <br />\n<br />\nDecember 2007: Jose Mourinho - &pound;23.1million <br />\n<br />\nMay 2008: Avram Grant - &pound;5.2million <br />\n<br />\nFebruary 2009: Luiz Felipe Scolari - &pound;12.6million <br />\n<br />\nMay 2011: Carlo Ancelotti - &pound;6million <br />\n<br />\nMarch 2012: Andre Villas-Boas - &pound;12million <br />\n<br />\nNovember 2012: Roberto Di Matteo - &pound;10.7million <br />\n<br />\nMay 2013: Rafa Benitez - WALKED<br />\n<br />\nDecember 2015: Jose Mourinho - &pound;8.3million <br />\n<br />\nMay 2016: Guus Hiddink - WALKED<br />\n<br />\nJuly 2018: Antonio Conte - &pound;26.6million*<br />\n<br />\nJune 2019: Maurizio Sarri - WALKED <br />\n<br />\nJanuary 2021: Frank Lampard - &pound;2million<br />\n<br />\nTotal: &pound;112.5million"},{"pid":"eebc2ba1a8202b9d03cdd89061696492d20f50e9","tid":2386975,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T03:27:54.